title: Hinterland - S01 E04 (Finale) - Sno
description:
Hinterland - S01 E04 (Finale) - Sno 


This was originally aired in 7 parts. The First Episode was broadcast whole - whilst the 3 other episodes were split into 2 parts. I have combined the split episodes together to make them complete.Well shot and heavily influenced by Scandinavian Drama.

Welsh speaking parts have Hardcoded Eng Subs

4/4 The body of a young woman in a striking red dress is found in Borth marshes - but the killer has arranged the corpse very carefully. Mathias is determined to get the culprit, but the case pushes him to the edge on both a personal and professional level. 
When Mathias and the team delve into Alys's complex social life, their findings lead them to a windswept Borth station. However, they find it difficult to differentiate between their suspect's true feelings and his professional persona. Last in the series.
